product_name: Carve Designs Fisher Bikini Top - Women's
long_description: If your idea of fun involves swimming, surfing or a tough game of beach volleyball, the Carve Designs Fisher Bikini Top offers an athletic fit and plenty of support so you don't have to hold back. Stretch-nylon fabric lets you dive for the ball or perfect that backflip off the dock. Built-in UPF 50+ sun protection shields skin from harmful ultraviolet rays. Carve Designs Fisher Bikini Top features a racerback design for an athletic look.
